long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: When searching for Spring Framework or Spring Boot docs, we often end up on the old version docs. With this extension, old reference gets a link at the top of the page taking you to the latest and greatest Spring docs!
